net.opentsdb.data.deserializers

Interface Deserializer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JSONDeserializer

    public interface Deserializer
    The interface used to describe a module that will deserialize raw bytes from the Kafka buss.

    Note that this class is implemented once per consumer group so make sure that calls to deserialize(KafkaRpcPluginThread, byte[]) are thread safe.

      • deserialize

        List<TypedIncomingData> deserialize(KafkaRpcPluginThread consumer,
                                    byte[] data)
        Deserialize the data into a list of zero or more TypedIncomingData points. If deserialization failed, catch the exception, log it and return null. Null data lists will increment the deserializationErrors counter.
        Parameters:
        consumer - A non-null consumer the data cam from.
        data - A non-null data byte array.
        Returns:
        A list of data points or null if deserialization failed.
